---
import SectionHeading from '../brand/SectionHeading.astro';
import Stamp from '../brand/Stamp.astro';
---

<section class="about container">
  <div class="about-stamp-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
    <Stamp size={280} />
  </div>
  <article class="about-card frosted">
    <SectionHeading text="Hello! I'm Marcos Koga!" />
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        Also known as Koga Noodle, your friendly Brazilian noodle dragon, and
        welcome to my corner of the internet!
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm a frontend developer with about two decades of experience under my
        belt, a variety streamer, and a creative explorer. I have always been
        driven by a need to express myself through different mediums, from
        drawing and dancing to my most recent passions: singing and 3D modeling
        in Blender.
      </p>
      <p>
        Streaming is one of my favorite forms of expression because I can blend
        my professional background with my content, building custom and
        interactive tools that allow my chat to engage with the stream in unique
        ways. Whether I'm diving into variety gaming, hanging out for a chill
        chat, or doing live development and experimentation, there's always
        something new happening here.
      </p>
      <p>
        When this noodle dragon leaves his cave, it's usually to travel with
        friends and visit them at big community events. I love hitting up
        conventions like FWA, Anthrocon, Midwest FurFest, and others.
      </p>
      <p class="rainbow-text">Thanks for stopping by!</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
  }

  .about-stamp-wrap {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 280px;
    opacity: 0.08;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    animation: stamp-drift 24s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes stamp-drift {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-4deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translate(-50%, -52%) rotate(4deg);
    }
  }

  .about-card {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 48rem;
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    animation: card-in 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.1s both;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-body p:last-child:not(.rainbow-text) {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @keyframes card-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(28px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-stamp-wrap {
      animation: none;
    }
    .about-card {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
